Sure, here are some examples of sentences that use the word "odmori" in different forms and positions:

1. *Odmori* se malo, umoran si. (Take a rest for a bit, you're tired.)
2. Moram da *odmorim* od posla. (I need to take a break from work.)
3. Ona je *odmorila* od napornog dana na plaži. (She rested from a tough day at the beach.)
4. *Odmor* ti je prekratak, treba ti više vremena za oporavak. (Your vacation is too short, you need more time to recover.)
5. Da li si dobro *odmorio* sinoć? (Did you rest well last night?)
6. Planiram da *odmorim* jedan dan ovog vikenda. (I plan to take a day off this weekend.)
7. U parku se nalazi *odmorište* za bicikliste. (There is a rest area for cyclists in the park.)
8. Potrebno mi je nekoliko dana *odmora* da se oporavim od bolesti. (I need a few days of rest to recover from illness.)
9. *Odmori* se, sve će biti u redu. (Relax, everything will be fine.)
10. Naši prijatelji planiraju da idu na *odmor* u Grčku. (Our friends are planning to go on vacation to Greece.)

Note: The word "odmori" is emphasized with an asterisk (*) in each sentence. The translations are provided in parentheses.